d":1915980,"uid":187726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5198052136d8445572c7f6c5b393e2cb30087d24","tid":1915980,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a459364957c96179316ebfa4e6ac525955a0ea1b","tid":1915980,"uid":53999,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98e9a37e9d07598b8d3d4179094464f68cc40507","tid":1915980,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:48:56.000Z","msg":"嵐山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"狗也不吊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T12:11:48.000Z","msg":"仲有咩景點好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"彥根城"},{"pid":"60ac5a7d7e2c8f28ef0a7b5a44a37fe4abf65a7c","tid":1915980,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T18:52:13.000Z","msg":"你去多幾次日本唔同地市, 其實來來去去都差唔多. 城堡, 花園, 坐艇仔, 廟, 表參道, &nbsp;溫泉區, 日式古老街道, 睇你鍾意睇乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九州可以坐吓火車買JR PASS , 由布院之森去由布院, 別府地獄溫泉好有特色, 順便去太宰府, 柳川坐艇仔. 有時間先去熊本 水前寺成趣園 都唔錯. <br />\n大阪去京都行下清水寺.嵐山.平日都好多遊客, 未去過值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,  買JR PASS 去 岡山 , 倉敷其實都係到此一遊冇咩特色, <br />\n北海道值得睇紅葉,破冰船,滑雪, 其他景點能取湖, 清池, 紋別海豹,水中展望台 都係一般, 反而飲牛奶,生果好正. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f7957f6c81300a07231b463ef3bad860bbf760","tid":1915980,"uid":168020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"去過大部分既日本城市 最中意都係東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffb7d63e1ffe4e7a1f6c95c549311e54bf75888","tid":1915980,"uid":181720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:10:09.000Z","msg":"有無東北+北海道嘅路線介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"